metadata.name: LUNAR
metadata.description:
From a place amongst the watch tower, there will always be someone looking down on you. whether its wrong or right, you must remember, some one will catch you when you fall, we as humans look to la luna, whether it be rocks, wolves, hunting material we can always find solace in the things we hold most dear to our hearts, this piece is to resemble to ground we walk on, air we breathe, moon we worship and most of all the next day within our sun, which helps the world grow..so take a step back and think to yourself, ''where have I been and what am i going to do next?''

Piece is a concept illustration and the first in this collection. It was digitally created with Vectors Rendered in 400DPI
